{"id":79365,"title":"Dizziness and vertigo.","abstract":"Dizziness is a common and challenging condition seen in the primary care office. Because dizziness is a vague term that can include a wide array of medical disorders, it is important to use a stepwise approach to differentiate between causes. This article focuses on vertigo and its four most common causes: benign paroxysmal peripheral vertigo, vestibular neuritis, vestibular migraine, and Meniere's disease. ","date":"2014-01-20","categories":"Otorhinolaryngologic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24439886","annotations":[{"name":"Migraine","weight":0.875066,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Migraine"},{"name":"Vertigo","weight":0.8337,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vertigo"},{"name":"Dizziness","weight":0.816298,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dizziness"},{"name":"Peripheral neuropathy","weight":0.79024,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peripheral_neuropathy"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.75303,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.479186,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Benignity","weight":0.394015,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benignity"},{"name":"Primary care","weight":0.347254,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primary_care"},{"name":"Vestibular system","weight":0.218348,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vestibular_system"},{"name":"Disorder (medicine)","weight":0.165844,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disorder_(medicine)"},{"name":"Vestibular neuronitis","weight":0.0574785,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vestibular_neuronitis"},{"name":"Peripheral","weight":0.0411186,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peripheral"},{"name":"Paroxysmal attack","weight":0.0355959,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paroxysmal_attack"},{"name":"Migraine-associated vertigo","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Migraine-associated_vertigo"},{"name":"Cellular differentiation","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cellular_differentiation"},{"name":"Array data structure","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Array_data_structure"},{"name":"Steps and skips","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steps_and_skips"}]}
